title: Tensions escalate after Syria downs Israeli jet
text:
Tensions escalate after Syria downs Israeli jet 11:52am EST - 01:20 
Israel has launched an attack against Syrian and Iranian targets in Syria after an Israeli fighter jet was shot down by Syrian anti-aircraft fire. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
